# Vutti Carbo Care - Environment Variables
# ----------------------------------------
# Since you are deploying to Vercel, you need a cloud database.
# We have configured the app to use Turso (libsql), a free serverless SQLite database.

# Step 1: Go to https://turso.tech and create a free account.
# Step 2: Create a database (e.g., `turso db create vutti-carbo`).
# Step 3: Get your Database URL (`turso db show --url vutti-carbo`).
# Step 4: Create an Auth Token (`turso db tokens create vutti-carbo`).
# Step 5: Add these to your Vercel Environment Variables.

# To test locally, you can create a `.env` file in the `frontend` folder with these:
TURSO_DATABASE_URL="libsql://your-database-url.turso.io"
TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN="your-auth-token"

# Optional: Twilio WhatsApp Setup
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=""
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=""
TWILIO_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=""
